<p><span style="color: purple"><tt>Hm. That's the right answer, and your bio-metrics seem to match up&#8230;Good morning,</tt></span> <tt><span style="color: green">Chairman Tejani.</span></tt></p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="color: green">input: And a good morning to you. I'd like to access the consensus regarding Primary Action.</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="color: purple"><tt>Of course. Just give me a moment&#8230;well, it looks like we're going to be having a new O5 Council, Chairman. Majority is in favour of Primary Action.</tt></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="color: green">input: I see.</span></p>
<blockquote>
