<p><strong>HELLENSTIC.AIC INTERNAL SYSTEMS ACCESSED.</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="color: grey"><tt>You're interfering with my systems.</tt></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
